Disable the in-app webtrees upgrade prompt.

The bundled docker image is immutable: bumping WEBTREES_VERSION is the
only supported upgrade path. Letting the admin UI's "upgrade now" button
run against an image-bound install would corrupt the tree.

--- a/app/Services/UpgradeService.php
+++ b/app/Services/UpgradeService.php
@@ -237,9 +237,8 @@ class UpgradeService
      */
     public function isUpgradeAvailable(bool $force = false): bool
     {
-        // If the latest version is unavailable, we will have an empty string which equates to version 0.
-
-        return version_compare(Webtrees::VERSION, $this->fetchLatestVersion($force)) < 0;
+        // Upgrade-lock: bundled image is immutable. See setup/patches/disable-upgrade-prompt.patch.
+        return false;
     }

